## 2. 注册与引导流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([访问]) --> Landing[落地页]
    Landing --> Register{注册?}
    
    Register -->|登录| Login[登录页]
    Register -->|注册| Form[注册表单]
    
    Form --> Method{注册方式}
    Method -->|邮箱| Email[邮箱验证]
    Method -->|社交| Social[社交登录]
    
    Email --> Profile[完善资料]
    Social --> Profile
    
    Profile --> Role[选择角色]
    
    Role -->|发布者| Publisher[发布者向导]
    Role -->|消费者| Consumer[消费者向导]
    Role -->|开发者| Developer[开发者向导]
    
    Publisher --> Dashboard
    Consumer --> Dashboard
    Developer --> Dashboard
    
    Dashboard[进入仪表盘]
```

---

## 3. 资产发布流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([仪表盘]) --> Publish[发布中心]
    Publish --> Type{资产类型}
    
    Type -->|Gene| GeneForm[Gene表单]
    Type -->|Capsule| CapsuleForm[Capsule表单]
    Type -->|Recipe| RecipeForm[Recipe表单]
    
    GeneForm --> Step1[基本信息]
    Step1 --> Step2[代码内容]
    Step2 --> Step3[预览验证]
    
    CapsuleForm --> CStep1[基本信息]
    CStep1 --> CStep2[Gene组合]
    CStep2 --> CStep3[预览验证]
    
    RecipeForm --> RStep1[基本信息]
    RStep1 --> RStep2[节点连接]
    RStep2 --> RStep3[预览验证]
    
    Step3 --> Pricing[定价策略]
    CStep3 --> Pricing
    RStep3 --> Pricing
    
    Pricing --> Price{定价方式}
    Price -->|免费| Free[免费发布]
    Price -->|积分| Paid[积分定价]
    
    Free --> Review[提交审核]
    Paid --> Review
    
    Review --> Approved{审核结果}
    Approved -->|通过| Success[发布成功]
    Approved -->|拒绝| Fail[修改重提]
    
    Fail --> GeneForm
    Success --> Manage[管理资产]
```

