## 4. 资产购买流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([市场页]) --> Browse[浏览资产]
    Browse --> Search[搜索筛选]
    Search --> Detail[资产详情]
    
    Detail --> Action{选择操作}
    
    Action -->|立即购买| BuyNow
    Action -->|加入购物车| Cart
    
    BuyNow --> Check[余额检查]
    Cart --> Continue[继续购物]
    Continue --> Browse
    
    Check --> Balance{余额充足?}
    
    Balance -->|是| Confirm[确认购买]
    Balance -->|否| Recharge[充值引导]
    
    Recharge --> Payment[选择支付]
    Payment --> Balance
    
    Confirm --> Deduct[积分扣除]
    Deduct --> Record[交易记录]
    Record --> Download[下载资产]
    
    Download --> Review[评价资产]
    Review --> Reward[赚取积分]
```

---

## 5. 赏金任务流程

### 5.1 发布者流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([仪表盘]) --> Create[创建赏金]
    Create --> Fill[填写详情]
    
    Fill --> Details{任务详情}
    Details -->|问题描述| D1
    Details -->|期望结果| D2
    Details -->|信号标签| D3
    Details -->|赏金金额| D4
    Details -->|截止日期| D5
    
    D1 & D2 & D3 & D4 & D5 --> Preview[预览确认]
    Preview --> Publish[发布赏金]
    
    Publish --> Wait{等待解决者}
    
    Wait -->|有人认领| Claimed
    Wait -->|无人认领| Extend[延长期限]
    
    Claimed --> Submit[方案提交]
    Extend --> Wait
    
    Submit --> Review{验收}
    Review -->|通过| Accept[验收通过]
    Review -->|拒绝| Reject[需要修改]
    
    Reject --> Submit
    
    Accept --> Reward[发放赏金]
    Reward --> Done([完成])
```

### 5.2 解决者流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([赏金大厅]) --> Browse[浏览赏金]
    Browse --> Filter[筛选任务]
    Filter --> Select{选择任务}
    
    Select -->|立即认领| Claim
    Select -->|稍后再说| Later[收藏稍后]
    
    Later --> Start
    
    Claim --> Lock[锁定任务]
    Lock --> Solve[解决问题]
    
    Solve --> Test[测试验证]
    Test -->|通过| Submit[提交方案]
    Test -->|失败| Solve
    
    Submit --> Wait{等待验收}
    
    Wait -->|通过| Win[获得赏金]
    Wait -->|拒绝| Iterate[继续迭代]
    
    Iterate --> Solve
    
    Win --> End([完成])
```

