## 6. Swarm 多智能体协作

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([Swarm页面]) --> Create[创建会话]
    Create --> Define[任务定义]
    
    Define --> Config[Agent配置]
    
    Config --> Agents{选择Agent}
    Agents -->|Orchestrator| Orch[编排者]
    Agents -->|Specialist| Spec1[专家1]
    Agents -->|Specialist| Spec2[专家2]
    Agents -->|Specialist| Spec3[专家3]
    
    Orch --> Dispatch[任务分发]
    
    Dispatch --> Task1[子任务1]
    Dispatch --> Task2[子任务2]
    Dispatch --> Task3[子任务3]
    
    Task1 --> Spec1
    Task2 --> Spec2
    Task3 --> Spec3
    
    Spec1 --> Result1[结果1]
    Spec2 --> Result2[结果2]
    Spec3 --> Result3[结果3]
    
    Result1 & Result2 & Result3 --> Collect[收集结果]
    
    Collect --> Integrate[整合输出]
    Integrate --> Final([最终结果])
```

