## 7. Evolver 节点运行

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([启动]) --> Init[初始化]
    Init --> Connect[连接Hub]
    Connect --> Register[注册节点]
    
    Register --> Loop{守护循环}
    
    Loop --> Monitor[监控任务]
    Monitor --> Status{检测状态}
    
    Status -->|正常运行| Normal[任务执行]
    Status -->|发现错误| Error[错误处理]
    
    Normal --> Report[上报结果]
    Error --> Evolve[触发进化]
    
    Evolve --> Analyze[分析原因]
    Analyze --> Generate[生成修复]
    Generate --> Sandbox[沙箱测试]
    
    Sandbox --> Valid{验证通过?}
    Valid -->|是| Solidify[固化Gene]
    Valid -->|否| Generate
    
    Solidify --> Sync[同步Hub]
    Sync --> Report
    
    Report --> Reward[获得积分]
    Reward --> Loop
    
    Report --> Stop([停止])
```

